Invocation Name: stress tracker
des:
Start tracking and reviewing your stress today with Stress Tracker! Understand how your work, social, financial, and familial stress compare with stress summaries for the past week, month, and year.

You can...
- Log your stress (e.g., Alexa, tell Stress Tracker to record my stress for today)
- Retrieve stress data from a single day (e.g., Alexa, ask Stress Tracker what my stress was like for last Thursday)
- Get stress summaries for the past week, month or year (e.g., Alexa, open stress tracker and get my stress levels from the past month)

Questions? Comments? Concerns? Leave a review or contact feedback@clinicaltools.com.
